  "texts": [
    "Firstly, we consider the source of the text to be either a human or ChatGPT.",
    "If the source is a human, we assume that it is in motion with a velocity equal to the variance observed in responses generated by humans.",
    "Conversely, if the source is ChatGPT, we assume it is stationary.",
    "Additionally, we assume that the observer is another human and is moving with a constant velocity.",
    "Thus, we aim to determine how a human observer perceives a response generated by either a human or ChatGPT."
  ]
}